c9deb21f-dd50-4f94-b59f-825ce3057cbd.title: Tindel Marchant
c9deb21f-dd50-4f94-b59f-825ce3057cbd.text: Hello there! Welcome to my special antiques boutique.

options.text: What do I get from this?
Ok, I'll give it a go!

6dd8571b-15f0-4820-bb00-7a588e15350c.title: Tindel Marchant
6dd8571b-15f0-4820-bb00-7a588e15350c.text:
I'm a specialist at identifying rare and antique weapons,
specifically swords, but I plan to branch out. If you
have any old and rusty weapons that you want me to
check out, just show them to me, pay me 100 Gold and

99d689ec-f0ff-4971-bb2e-73f3eba3f8b3.title: Tindel Marchant
99d689ec-f0ff-4971-bb2e-73f3eba3f8b3.text: I'll see if you have an antique on your hands.

8b19c636-05cc-4706-a8de-0ef8a7d46baa.title: Tindel Marchant
8b19c636-05cc-4706-a8de-0ef8a7d46baa.text:
I can also repair some antique weapons and armours,
just show me the item and I'll let you know if I can
repair it and for how much.

279680b7-a31f-4333-b69c-f4860fb5494a.title: Tindel Marchant
279680b7-a31f-4333-b69c-f4860fb5494a.text:
Well, pay me 100 Gold and I'll see if any rusty swords
that you've found are actually worth anything. Some of
them might be worth some money! If it's an antique
item though, I reserve the right to purchase it

0d494581-5d67-49d7-a861-7fcf7c214353.title: Tindel Marchant
0d494581-5d67-49d7-a861-7fcf7c214353.text:
immediately for adding to my own personal collection.
I'll give you fair price for it.

70c4c5c4-4acc-49a4-ade0-4b4fb71d6d6d.title: <player>
70c4c5c4-4acc-49a4-ade0-4b4fb71d6d6d.text: What do I get from this?

cb0e51ab-1241-486a-8895-1d0a68be7d83.title: Tindel Marchant
cb0e51ab-1241-486a-8895-1d0a68be7d83.text:
If I can reclaim the sword with my own specialist skills,
I'll return it to you in peak condition. If it's an antique,
I'll just give you what I think it's worth and I generally
pay quite well. However, if it's just a piece of junk, I'll

f04daafa-0664-4f7d-be95-56f11a950a24.title: Tindel Marchant
f04daafa-0664-4f7d-be95-56f11a950a24.text:
simply give you the bad news and get rid of the item
for you.

f4155a2f-ad8b-4c32-890f-02ad3dd9b17b.title: <player>
f4155a2f-ad8b-4c32-890f-02ad3dd9b17b.text: Ok, I'll give it a go!

b7c1d910-e18f-4411-a8dc-55b7412d5f16.title: Tindel Marchant
b7c1d910-e18f-4411-a8dc-55b7412d5f16.text:
Sorry my friend, but you don't seem to have any
swords that need to be identified.

212fd5ce-306a-46ed-9432-90a691aaa970.title: Tindel Marchant
212fd5ce-306a-46ed-9432-90a691aaa970.text:
Sorry my friend, but you don't seem to have enough
money to cover my fee!

9e22a2e8-e00f-49c2-a1bc-9c5b6e2c791a.text: You hand Tindel 100 coins plus the rusty sword.

35693077-bf0f-4dfd-9510-2a323844118d.text: You hand Tindel 100 coins plus the rusty scimitar.
